&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Resource &amp;amp; Toolkit Development:&lt;/strong&gt; Create practical, actionable guides, checklists, and toolkits that empower people managers to easily embed inclusive leadership practices into daily team workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
