&lt;p&gt;Do you want to play a major role in the future of public media? Do you have a passion for mobile technology, open-source software, and serving the public?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As our Mobile Software Engineering Manager on the Audience Technology team, you will lead a highly collaborative team of mobile software engineers building, testing, and delivering award-winning features for NPR&#39;s flagship mobile applications. You will partner closely with our Product, Design, Data, and Editorial teams to identify priorities, architect new features, and continuously improve existing applications. In this role, you will act as a primary champion of team health, career progression, and technical excellence.&lt;/p&gt;
